<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hire-n">hire <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'haɪə(r)/    美 /'haɪər/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>租用；雇用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>let out sth on hire 
出租某物</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cars <strong>on / for hire</strong> 
供租用的汽车</p></div></div>